reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 8, 2024
reviews.reviewText: LOVE this. Just received it and is great. Easy to put on and makes my gold phone look like it's a lavender color. Great protection for my phone as well!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 27, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars The screen protector blocks the fingerprint sensing
reviews.reviewText: I mostly wanted the case, but it came with a screen protector, so I installed it. The screen protector was fairly thick compared with others I've used, so I was skeptical. Sure enough, the fingerprint sensor on the screen no longer worked. I removed the protector and discarded it.The main case has two parts: a frame and a silcone backer. You first install the frame and then the backer. This adds a little bulk to the phone which I would have preferred not to have, but I can live with it. I suppose it helps protect better against falls. I had a hard time finding printed patterns I liked, so that's why I selected this one. I liked the look.It also came with a stick-on protector for the camera lenses. I installed it, but I'm not sure why it's needed. The lenses on the phone already have a glass protector built-in. So now there are two layers of glass. I don't notice any image degradation. I suppose if this protector gets scratched, I can peel it off and be back to the original protection that came with the phone.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 3, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Pretty Case with Full Protection
reviews.reviewText: Case fit on securely and feels fine to hold. The material of the case isn't very grippy but not slippery either. The rear camera screen protector has not affected image quality to any discernable degree. All the ports and the side buttons are easily accessible and work. The only annoying thing was applying the front screen protector. You just kind of wing it. There's no plastic frame to align it perfectly. Luckily, the adhesive isn't super strong and you can remove it and align as much as you want in the beginning. It is glass so it does not bend. Had it for about a week so will see how it holds up in time but so far it's doing the job!Oh also the fingerprint sensor is not affected with this protector. If anyone else is having issues with that, in Settings under Display there's a Touch Sensitivity setting that you should turn on. It is on for this phone and there aren't issues unlocking it. Still reads fingerprint very quick.
